# Keeps aider's repo map lean. NOTE aider's real semantics: it REFUSES to /add
# any path matched here (there is no manual-add escape hatch). The bug-lock
# workflow (AGENTS.md: traces/bugs/ artifact + tests/regression/ test) and
# quest-pack editing therefore need a tool that can see those paths (Claude
# Code / Codex) — do not attempt them via aider with this file in place.
node_modules/
dist/
coverage/
ai-runs/
blind-tester/reports/
.agent-cleaner/
.codex/*
!.codex/config.toml
saves/
transcripts/
*.log
*.tmp
*.tsbuildinfo

AI_LOOP_STATE_ARCHIVE.md
ADVENTUREFORGE_BUILD_SPEC.md
docs/DECISION_LOG.md
docs/archive/
package-lock.json
ui/package-lock.json
content/world/new_york_overworld.json
content/rpg/quests/*.yaml
traces/
corpus/
tests/regression/
